Description: Kernel Update Utility for Ubuntu-based distributions
 Utility for installing mainline Linux kernels on Ubuntu-based distributions.
 Downloads and installs kernel packages from kernel.ubuntu.com.
 .
 This is a fork and continuation of the final GPL version of the original author's package "ukuu".
